---
// src/components/AboutUs.astro
// Modern About Us section with dark mode support
---

<section id="nosotros" class="relative py-20 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background with gradient glow -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
        <!-- Gradient glow effects -->
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-sky-500/10 dark:bg-sky-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/10 dark:bg-blue-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>

        <!-- Subtle pattern overlay -->
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.015] dark:opacity-[0.02]"
            style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgb(0 0 0) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
        <!-- Two-column layout on desktop -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 mb-16 lg:mb-20">
            <!-- Left: Text content -->
            <div class="space-y-6" data-reveal="fade-up">
                <!-- Badge -->
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-600 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/60 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 border border-zinc-200/60 dark:border-white/10"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-4 h-4"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                    Nosotros
                </div>

                <!-- Headline -->
                <h2
                    id="about-title"
                    class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-700 tracking-tight leading-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100"
                    data-reveal="fade-up"
                    data-delay="80"
                >
                    Somos 3 jóvenes ingenieros informáticos de la Cuarta Región
                </h2>

                <!-- Paragraph -->
                <p
                    class="text-lg font-400 leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300"
                    data-reveal="fade-up"
                    data-delay="160"
                >
                    Al terminar de estudiar, decidimos crear una pyme para
                    ayudar a negocios locales a crecer en Internet con una
                    presencia moderna, rápida y confiable. Partimos trabajando
                    con restaurantes, tiendas y pymes que necesitaban actualizar
                    su imagen, fortalecer su marca y aumentar la confianza de
                    sus clientes.
                </p>

                <!-- Optional tagline -->
                <p
                    class="text-sm font-500 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"
                    data-reveal="fade-up"
                    data-delay="240"
                >
                    Equipo local • Enfoque práctico • Resultados medibles
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: Visual element (decorative graphic) -->
            <div class="relative" data-reveal="fade-up" data-delay="200">
                <div
                    class="relative aspect-square lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/10 via-blue-500/5 to-indigo-500/10 dark:from-sky-400/5 dark:via-blue-400/3 dark:to-indigo-400/5 border border-zinc-200/60 dark:border-white/10 p-8 lg:p-12 flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                    <!-- Abstract shapes representing team/technology -->
                    <div class="relative w-full h-full">
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-24 h-24 bg-sky-500/20 dark:bg-sky-400/10 rounded-full blur-xl"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/3 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/20 dark:bg-blue-400/10 rounded-full blur-xl"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-40 h-40 border-2 border-zinc-300/40 dark:border-white/10 rounded-full"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-28 h-28 border-2 border-zinc-400/30 dark:border-white/5 rounded-full"
                        >
                        </div>

                        <!-- Icon/symbol in center -->
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-16 h-16"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Three pillars grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8" data-stagger="children">
            <!-- Pillar 1 -->
            <div
                data-reveal="fade-up"
                class="group relative p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 dark:bg-zinc-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-zinc-200/60 dark:border-white/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-zinc-900/5 dark:hover:shadow-black/20"
            >
                <div
                    class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-sky-500/10 dark:bg-sky-400/10 text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-600 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2"
                >
                    Cercanía real
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-base font-400 leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300"
                >
                    Hablamos simple, te acompañamos y resolvemos rápido.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Pillar 2 -->
            <div
                data-reveal="fade-up"
                class="group relative p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 dark:bg-zinc-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-zinc-200/60 dark:border-white/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-zinc-900/5 dark:hover:shadow-black/20"
            >
                <div
                    class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 dark:bg-blue-400/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-600 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2"
                >
                    Diseño + performance
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-base font-400 leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300"
                >
                    Sitios rápidos, claros y pensados para convertir.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Pillar 3 -->
            <div
                data-reveal="fade-up"
                class="group relative p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 dark:bg-zinc-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-zinc-200/60 dark:border-white/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-zinc-900/5 dark:hover:shadow-black/20"
            >
                <div
                    class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 dark:bg-indigo-400/10 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-600 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2"
                >
                    Orden y entrega
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-base font-400 leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300"
                >
                    Plan de trabajo, avances visibles y entregas a tiempo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
